      "id": "prior-api-key-setup",
      "name": "Guided LLM API key setup",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-19</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>6275307</code></li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +159 / -32</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> (prior session &mdash; not measured)</li></ul><p>Step-by-step in-app instructions for obtaining and pasting an API key for each supported LLM provider, surfaced inside the Settings dialog.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "prior-sessions",
      "childrenIds": [],
