      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-19</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>3688849</code></li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +112 / -1</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> (prior session &mdash; not measured)</li></ul><p>Added a key-management section to the Settings dialog and fixed dialog scrolling.</p>",
