      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-15</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>5528483</code></li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +37 / -7</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> (prior session &mdash; not measured)</li></ul><p>Three correctness fixes to iOS gesture handling and layout behavior in the node tree.</p>",
