    "prior-gemma4-migration": {
      "id": "prior-gemma4-migration",
      "name": "Migrate local AI from llama3.2 to Gemma 4",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-10</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>3625bfc</code></li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 15</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +947 / -115</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> (prior session &mdash; not measured)</li></ul><p>Replaced the default local model with Gemma 4 across every Ollama call path, plus a dedicated Playwright smoke test that validates the model is reachable and answering.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "prior-sessions",
