    "prior-ai-image-descriptions": {
      "id": "prior-ai-image-descriptions",
      "name": "AI image descriptions and backup redesign",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-03</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>1b3850d</code></li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +189 / -71</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> (prior session &mdash; not measured)</li></ul><p>Added AI-generated image descriptions, redesigned the backup / restore flow, and cleaned up the Generate menu structure.</p>",
